cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with language models and their representation as weighted finite automata. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper involves optimization techniques for approximating probabilistic models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with building models for language processing tasks. 
- cs.SD (Sound) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are less likely categories, but cannot be completely ruled out as the paper involves algorithms and data structures for representing probabilistic models.
